WEBVTT

00:01:17.800 --> 00:01:18.560
I will pay you back.

00:01:18.560 --> 00:01:19.890
I didn't say I wouldn't.

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:21.240
But your interest rate is really too high.

00:01:21.240 --> 00:01:22.240
Let's discuss it.

00:01:24.520 --> 00:01:26.180
How are we going to discuss it?

00:01:26.800 --> 00:01:29.400
You asked Eryong to come and discuss it with me?

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:30.680
Do you think Eryong

00:01:30.680 --> 00:01:33.200
has influence on this street,

00:01:33.960 --> 00:01:35.690
and you want him to pressure me?

00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:38.000
No, no, no.

00:01:38.440 --> 00:01:40.300
I just want to discuss it with you.

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:46.060
Let me tell you.

00:01:46.920 --> 00:01:48.280
Eryong on this street

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:50.320
is nothing but a lousy bouncer.

00:01:51.759 --> 00:01:53.360
You asking him to pressure me

00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:56.120
is an insult to me.

00:01:56.920 --> 00:01:57.600
Brothers.

00:01:57.600 --> 00:01:59.600
Your boss got scolded.

00:01:59.640 --> 00:02:00.480
What should we do?

00:02:00.480 --> 00:02:01.280
Teach him a lesson.

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:01.760
Yeah.

00:02:02.720 --> 00:02:03.160
Hao.

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:03.930
Please, Hao.

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:04.560
Hao.

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:05.360
I really don't have

00:02:05.360 --> 00:02:05.880
any money right now.

00:02:05.880 --> 00:02:07.240
Hao, I'm begging you.

00:02:07.240 --> 00:02:08.440
Hao, I'm begging you.

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:09.680
Hao, I'm begging you.

00:02:09.680 --> 00:02:10.240
Lift,

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:10.759
lift it up.

00:02:10.759 --> 00:02:12.240
Brother Hao, I beg you!

00:02:13.920 --> 00:02:15.760
Don't scare our friend here.

00:02:16.200 --> 00:02:17.600
What are you yelling for?

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:19.140
No one is going to kill you.

00:02:20.280 --> 00:02:20.920
Brother,

00:02:21.520 --> 00:02:22.720
I'm helping you

00:02:22.880 --> 00:02:24.720
get promoted and strike it rich.

00:02:28.079 --> 00:02:28.800
Brother.

00:02:30.079 --> 00:02:31.400
I'll carve a pair of

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:33.920
auspicious dragons and phoenixes for you.

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:34.680
How about it?

00:02:37.560 --> 00:02:38.160
Enough.

00:02:38.200 --> 00:02:39.160
Hao, I can pay.

00:02:39.160 --> 00:02:39.680
Hao!

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:40.880
Hao, I'll pay. Hao, I'll pay.

00:02:40.880 --> 00:02:42.240
Hao, I'll pay. I promise.

00:02:42.240 --> 00:02:42.920
Hao, I beg you.

00:02:42.920 --> 00:02:43.840
Hao, just give me a few more days.

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:44.640
I'm begging you, Hao.

00:02:44.640 --> 00:02:45.520
I have a family to support.

00:02:45.520 --> 00:02:46.560
I can't die, Hao!

00:02:46.640 --> 00:02:49.560
Hao!

00:02:52.079 --> 00:02:53.079
We always thought

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:54.560
that Ma Jinguang became a suspect

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:56.240
because of our investigation.

00:02:56.240 --> 00:02:57.800
But what if we look at it from another angle?

00:02:57.800 --> 00:02:59.120
What if he became a suspect

00:02:59.120 --> 00:03:00.120
because the killer

00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:01.080
set it up for us?

00:03:02.120 --> 00:03:02.650
Exactly.

00:03:03.040 --> 00:03:04.570
If the killer knew all along

00:03:04.600 --> 00:03:07.000
that Ma Jinguang was making explosives in the cabin.

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:08.760
So he specifically asked Ma Jinguang to customize

00:03:08.760 --> 00:03:10.280
the bomb that killed Zhang Biao.

00:03:10.280 --> 00:03:10.720
Ah.

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:14.440
Is the item I asked for ready?

00:03:14.960 --> 00:03:17.160
I've left the money at the agreed place.

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:18.560
Moreover,

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:20.560
after kidnapping Wang Hongjia,

00:03:20.560 --> 00:03:22.480
he went to great lengths to first take her

00:03:22.480 --> 00:03:23.880
to the cabin for torture,

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:26.560
and then deliberately transferred her from there.

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:27.220
The purpose

00:03:27.240 --> 00:03:28.240
was to make sure the cabin

00:03:28.240 --> 00:03:30.440
had traces of Ma Jinguang making bombs,

00:03:30.560 --> 00:03:33.420
as well as kidnapping and assaulting Wang Hongjia.

00:03:36.320 --> 00:03:37.440
Everything he did

00:03:38.200 --> 00:03:39.920
was just to frame Ma Jinguang.

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:44.840
The tech department found fragments of the detonator

00:03:44.840 --> 00:03:46.800
and discovered traces of two ignition points on them.

00:03:46.800 --> 00:03:48.960
The detonating cord that actually set off the explosives

00:03:48.960 --> 00:03:49.920
had already been removed.

00:03:49.920 --> 00:03:51.120
From this, we can infer

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:52.480
that the person who caused the mine explosion

00:03:52.480 --> 00:03:53.610
was not Ma Jinguang.

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:55.440
They also analyzed that footprint.

00:03:55.440 --> 00:03:58.040
Although the uneven footprint of a limp can be imitated,

00:03:58.040 --> 00:04:00.100
height and weight cannot be changed.

00:04:00.440 --> 00:04:01.160
Preliminary analysis indicates

00:04:01.160 --> 00:04:02.280
that the height of the suspect

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:04.440
is between 1.76 and 1.79 meters.

00:04:04.640 --> 00:04:06.170
Weighs about 70 kilograms.

00:04:07.600 --> 00:04:09.320
1.76 to 1.79 meters tall.

00:04:09.520 --> 00:04:09.640
I also investigated the technical

00:04:09.640 --> 00:04:10.480
I also investigated

00:04:10.480 --> 00:04:10.840
Authorized signatory:

00:04:10.840 --> 00:04:12.280
the account that contacted Ma Jinguang online

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:13.680
and made the transaction.

00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:15.810
But he used multiple proxy addresses.

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:18.300
We can't trace his real IP address at all.

00:04:18.920 --> 00:04:19.839
Among them,

00:04:20.240 --> 00:04:21.880
one of his IP addresses is...

00:04:24.680 --> 00:04:25.340
Where is it?

00:04:30.440 --> 00:04:31.640
No. 3 Zhongshan Road.

00:04:31.760 --> 00:04:33.490
Right across from our station.

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:36.330
Captain Sun.

00:04:38.120 --> 00:04:39.720
Sister Zhen asked me to bring the test report.

00:04:39.720 --> 00:04:40.400
The report shows

00:04:40.400 --> 00:04:42.040
the sawdust in the footprints is golden-thread nanmu.

00:04:42.040 --> 00:04:42.520
Also,

00:04:42.520 --> 00:04:44.800
based on the autopsy analysis of Wang Hongjia,

00:04:44.800 --> 00:04:45.480
what cut her

00:04:45.480 --> 00:04:46.640
should be a carpenter's hand knife.

00:04:46.640 --> 00:04:47.240
In the wound,

00:04:47.240 --> 00:04:50.280
trace amounts of golden-thread nanmu sawdust were also detected.

00:04:50.280 --> 00:04:51.159
Golden-thread nanmu

00:04:51.159 --> 00:04:52.600
is a national Class II protected plant.

00:04:52.600 --> 00:04:53.480
It's expensive

00:04:53.920 --> 00:04:55.720
and generally used for high-end solid wood furniture.

00:04:55.720 --> 00:04:56.240
And

00:04:59.040 --> 00:04:59.800
on coffins.

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:06.840
When I was reconstructing Ma Jinguang's movements,

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:08.370
I found that he had visited a

00:05:08.400 --> 00:05:09.130
coffin shop.

00:05:09.880 --> 00:05:11.010
I initially thought

00:05:11.120 --> 00:05:12.680
he was making funeral arrangements for Kong Jiao,

00:05:12.680 --> 00:05:14.410
so I didn't pay much attention.

00:06:09.240 --> 00:06:09.760
Boss.

00:06:10.880 --> 00:06:12.410
Do you have the best coffin?

00:06:12.960 --> 00:06:13.640
Oh.

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:16.520
Welcome, honored guest.

00:06:16.680 --> 00:06:18.680
Excuse my lack of a proper greeting.

00:06:18.880 --> 00:06:20.340
Although my shop is small,

00:06:20.800 --> 00:06:21.680
I have coffins

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:23.000
of all kinds.

00:06:23.800 --> 00:06:24.800
Big or small,

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:25.720
long or short,

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:27.320
made of Chinese fir or nanmu.

00:06:27.320 --> 00:06:28.520
Sandalwood,

00:06:28.640 --> 00:06:29.770
we have everything.

00:06:30.360 --> 00:06:31.480
Take a look at this.

00:06:31.760 --> 00:06:33.640
I carved the flowers myself.

00:06:34.280 --> 00:06:35.400
It's a work of art.

00:06:36.440 --> 00:06:37.159
Distinguished guest,

00:06:37.159 --> 00:06:37.840
You.

00:06:39.320 --> 00:06:40.440
Which one do you fancy?

00:06:40.440 --> 00:06:42.000
What are you talking about?

00:06:42.320 --> 00:06:44.240
What do you mean which one I like?

00:06:44.280 --> 00:06:44.760
Oh.

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:48.280
I'm seeing my brother off on his final journey.

00:06:48.640 --> 00:06:50.970
I definitely want the most expensive one.

00:06:51.400 --> 00:06:52.240
Okay, okay.

00:06:55.680 --> 00:06:56.080
Here.

00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:58.130
This is the deposit.

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:01.220
I'll come pick it up in three days.

00:07:01.640 --> 00:07:02.800
Thanks for your trouble.

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:03.480
Okay.

00:07:04.120 --> 00:07:05.780
I'll work overtime overnight

00:07:05.960 --> 00:07:08.820
to carve you another pair of dragons and phoenixes.

00:07:09.080 --> 00:07:09.920
Great.

00:07:10.640 --> 00:07:11.480
Thanks for your trouble.

00:07:11.480 --> 00:07:12.240
Ah, okay.

00:07:13.400 --> 00:07:14.160
Take care.

00:07:21.960 --> 00:07:22.800
Take care.

00:07:22.880 --> 00:07:24.410
Take care, esteemed guest.

00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:16.810
Captain Sun.

00:08:17.280 --> 00:08:17.920
What's up?

00:08:19.880 --> 00:08:21.000
Where is Hao Weiguo?

00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:21.720
Bro,

00:08:22.440 --> 00:08:23.400
he was just here.

00:08:23.640 --> 00:08:24.840
He probably went out.

00:08:25.400 --> 00:08:26.530
What a coincidence.

00:09:12.480 --> 00:09:13.210
Hao the Lame.

00:09:14.120 --> 00:09:15.040
An old friend is here.

00:09:15.040 --> 00:09:15.800
Aren't you coming out

00:09:15.800 --> 00:09:16.730
to entertain me?

00:09:17.320 --> 00:09:17.840
Oh.

00:09:17.960 --> 00:09:19.840
I was dreaming.

00:09:22.280 --> 00:09:23.280
Sleeping in here?

00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:24.500
Can you even sleep?

00:09:24.800 --> 00:09:26.280
I slept very well.

00:09:26.720 --> 00:09:28.180
It's only a matter of time.

00:09:30.560 --> 00:09:31.240
Ermao,

00:09:31.800 --> 00:09:32.680
make Captain Sun

00:09:32.680 --> 00:09:33.840
a good cup of tea.

00:09:34.040 --> 00:09:34.640
No, no, no.

00:09:34.800 --> 00:09:35.660
How about this?

00:09:35.840 --> 00:09:37.360
Come back to the station with me,

00:09:37.360 --> 00:09:39.020
and I'll treat you to some tea.

00:09:39.240 --> 00:09:40.160
Forget it.

00:09:41.080 --> 00:09:41.560
Ah.

00:09:45.760 --> 00:09:46.320
Wait.

00:10:12.520 --> 00:10:13.250
Captain Sun,

00:10:14.400 --> 00:10:16.200
is this how you invite me for tea?

00:10:16.520 --> 00:10:17.180
Hao Weiguo.

00:10:17.520 --> 00:10:18.720
My name is Hao Weiguo.

00:10:18.840 --> 00:10:19.320
Four.

00:10:23.920 --> 00:10:26.320
You haven't forgotten the prison rules at all.

00:10:26.320 --> 00:10:27.780
We are old acquaintances.

00:10:27.880 --> 00:10:29.080
You know the procedure.

00:10:29.080 --> 00:10:31.640
Do I have to squeeze it out of you, or will you tell me everything?

00:10:31.640 --> 00:10:32.370
Captain Sun,

00:10:32.960 --> 00:10:34.240
we are good friends.

00:10:34.960 --> 00:10:37.090
Of course, I will tell you everything.

00:10:37.240 --> 00:10:38.640
But what can I say?

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:40.320
I'm still confused.

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:43.120
I don't even know what I did.

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:43.970
Alright.

00:10:44.160 --> 00:10:45.440
Still making us drag it out of you.

00:10:45.440 --> 00:10:45.880
Here.

00:10:47.120 --> 00:10:48.180
Take a look at this.

00:10:49.600 --> 00:10:50.860
What's this all about?

00:10:58.400 --> 00:11:00.330
Think carefully before you speak.

00:11:00.840 --> 00:11:02.900
We've already checked your toolbox.

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:04.240
And it just so happens

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:06.120
to be missing one.

00:11:07.440 --> 00:11:08.720
Th-This knife...

00:11:08.880 --> 00:11:10.120
I-It's mine.

00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:13.400
But I don't know anything about the blood on it.

00:11:13.960 --> 00:11:14.960
I'm a carpenter.

00:11:15.640 --> 00:11:17.240
I only carve wood, not people.

00:11:17.240 --> 00:11:19.120
How do you know it's blood?

00:11:21.880 --> 00:11:23.160
Whose blood is it?

00:11:23.160 --> 00:11:25.760
You're really underestimating us craftsmen.

00:11:26.040 --> 00:11:28.170
I've been doing this for so many years.

00:11:28.560 --> 00:11:30.720
Whether it's paint or blood,

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:33.000
even a child could tell.

00:11:33.320 --> 00:11:34.400
But I swear,

00:11:34.520 --> 00:11:35.360
this knife,

00:11:35.360 --> 00:11:36.680
it really is mine.

00:11:37.400 --> 00:11:38.600
But whose blood this is,

00:11:38.600 --> 00:11:39.730
I really don't know.

00:11:40.160 --> 00:11:42.200
Even though I sell coffins,

00:11:42.680 --> 00:11:45.040
it doesn't mean I have no taboos.

00:11:45.120 --> 00:11:48.200
If the tools of my trade get blood on them,

00:11:48.200 --> 00:11:50.120
that's a huge taboo.

00:11:50.120 --> 00:11:51.520
So what you mean is,

00:11:51.720 --> 00:11:53.400
the blood on this knife,

00:11:53.400 --> 00:11:55.130
you don't know how it got there.

00:11:55.440 --> 00:11:56.440
I don't know.

00:12:08.680 --> 00:12:09.410
This person,

00:12:09.760 --> 00:12:10.620
do you know him?

00:12:11.840 --> 00:12:12.640
I've seen him.

00:12:12.720 --> 00:12:14.250
He came to my shop yesterday

00:12:14.320 --> 00:12:15.560
and ordered a coffin

00:12:16.280 --> 00:12:17.880
made of golden thread nanmu.

00:12:28.120 --> 00:12:28.980
What about her?

00:12:29.200 --> 00:12:30.480
Isn't this Sister Jia,

00:12:30.800 --> 00:12:31.800
A Biao's wife?

00:12:32.560 --> 00:12:33.820
She used to work at Arc,

00:12:33.840 --> 00:12:35.300
managing the young girls.

00:12:35.440 --> 00:12:35.840
Hey,

00:12:36.080 --> 00:12:37.480
let me ask you something.

00:12:37.760 --> 00:12:39.720
I heard that a while ago,

00:12:39.760 --> 00:12:40.600
A Biao

00:12:40.640 --> 00:12:43.240
was suddenly blown up by some enemy.

00:12:43.840 --> 00:12:44.720
Is that true?

00:12:45.120 --> 00:12:46.640
I wanted to go ask Sister Jia

00:12:46.640 --> 00:12:47.440
to come to my shop

00:12:47.440 --> 00:12:49.900
and buy some coffin materials or something.

00:12:51.480 --> 00:12:52.440
Qiao Sisi

00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:53.680
and Kong Jiao,

00:12:53.920 --> 00:12:55.120
you know them, right?

00:12:57.000 --> 00:12:57.660
I know them.

00:12:58.120 --> 00:12:59.840
They were the top girls at Arc.

00:13:00.400 --> 00:13:01.280
Before,

00:13:01.280 --> 00:13:02.120
I had a little bit of

00:13:02.120 --> 00:13:03.560
interaction with them.

00:13:03.800 --> 00:13:05.480
Those two,

00:13:05.520 --> 00:13:07.560
they had the looks

00:13:07.560 --> 00:13:10.360
and the bodies.

00:13:10.720 --> 00:13:11.240
Well,

00:13:13.040 --> 00:13:13.840
wait a minute.

00:13:15.520 --> 00:13:16.880
Aren't they dead?

00:13:18.120 --> 00:13:18.850
Captain Sun,

00:13:19.560 --> 00:13:21.200
you don't suspect their matter

00:13:21.200 --> 00:13:22.920
has anything to do with me, do you?

00:13:22.920 --> 00:13:24.360
From May 15th to 18th,

00:13:24.440 --> 00:13:25.080
where were you?

00:13:25.080 --> 00:13:25.680
The provincial capital.

00:13:25.680 --> 00:13:26.520
I was in the city

00:13:26.520 --> 00:13:27.160
attending

00:13:27.160 --> 00:13:29.680
a training by the Arts and Crafts Association.

00:13:29.680 --> 00:13:30.240
What?

00:13:30.320 --> 00:13:31.280
You answered so quickly,

00:13:31.280 --> 00:13:32.120
without even thinking about it.

00:13:32.120 --> 00:13:34.280
Don't I want to inherit the family business?

00:13:34.280 --> 00:13:36.520
I want to carry forward my wood carving.

00:13:37.040 --> 00:13:38.770
So I signed up for the training.

00:13:39.040 --> 00:13:40.040
Twenty thousand.

00:13:40.640 --> 00:13:41.560
I heard

00:13:42.040 --> 00:13:43.720
there's a test at the end.

00:13:44.320 --> 00:13:45.800
Can you issue me

00:13:46.120 --> 00:13:48.800
a district-level woodcarver certificate?

00:13:50.040 --> 00:13:51.320
And after you came back from the provincial capital?

00:13:51.320 --> 00:13:52.160
I was in the shop.

00:13:52.160 --> 00:13:52.840
What else did you do?

00:13:52.840 --> 00:13:53.560
Played cards

00:13:53.560 --> 00:13:54.400
with friends.

00:13:54.640 --> 00:13:56.720
Played every day like it was a job.

00:13:56.720 --> 00:13:57.600
Who can vouch for you?

00:13:57.600 --> 00:13:58.160
Lao Jin,

00:13:58.920 --> 00:13:59.480
Lao Yuan.

00:14:00.080 --> 00:14:01.410
Ermao can also prove it.

00:14:12.080 --> 00:14:12.680
Everyone,

00:14:13.080 --> 00:14:14.400
the footprints at the crime scene

00:14:14.400 --> 00:14:15.880
don't match Hao Weiguo's.

00:14:16.560 --> 00:14:18.000
The biggest difference is

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:18.840
that his shoes

00:14:19.040 --> 00:14:20.120
are custom-made.

00:14:20.600 --> 00:14:21.720
Inside his left shoe,

00:14:21.720 --> 00:14:22.360
there is

00:14:22.520 --> 00:14:23.640
an elevator insole.

00:14:23.640 --> 00:14:25.080
This balances his height

00:14:25.080 --> 00:14:26.760
and relieves his limp.

00:14:27.880 --> 00:14:30.240
However, the footprints we found near the mine

00:14:30.240 --> 00:14:31.480
are completely different

00:14:31.480 --> 00:14:32.540
from Hao Weiguo's.

00:14:33.240 --> 00:14:34.560
We can basically conclude

00:14:34.560 --> 00:14:36.760
that the footprints are not Hao Weiguo's.

00:14:36.760 --> 00:14:37.320
Perhaps

00:14:37.320 --> 00:14:38.960
the killer didn't think of this,

00:14:38.960 --> 00:14:40.200
so they made a mistake

00:14:40.280 --> 00:14:41.280
when copying him.

00:14:43.360 --> 00:14:46.820
Does that mean Hao Weiguo is completely cleared of suspicion?

00:14:48.920 --> 00:14:49.800
Go verify

00:14:49.800 --> 00:14:51.160
Hao Weiguo's alibi.

00:14:51.360 --> 00:14:52.760
If there are no problems,

00:14:53.520 --> 00:14:54.450
let him go first.

00:15:04.360 --> 00:15:05.160
So who exactly

00:15:07.600 --> 00:15:08.640
is the killer?

00:15:14.320 --> 00:15:15.320
I really miss you.

00:15:16.200 --> 00:15:18.130
But I went against your teachings.

00:15:42.520 --> 00:15:43.440
You have found

00:15:43.800 --> 00:15:44.600
your truth.

00:15:46.520 --> 00:15:48.520
I wasn't the one who found the truth.

00:15:48.680 --> 00:15:49.360
It was you.

00:15:50.880 --> 00:15:52.240
I will bear what I must.

00:15:52.920 --> 00:15:53.840
I will take

00:15:54.280 --> 00:15:54.940
what I must.

00:15:55.960 --> 00:15:56.920
Master, Madam,

00:15:57.440 --> 00:15:58.120
and you,

00:15:59.160 --> 00:16:00.820
I will spend the rest of my life

00:16:02.120 --> 00:16:03.480
slowly making amends

00:16:06.640 --> 00:16:07.560
for this.

00:16:22.280 --> 00:16:24.760
Ma Jinguang finally got what he deserved.

00:16:25.440 --> 00:16:27.770
He played with fire and got burned, right?

00:16:28.440 --> 00:16:29.240
His case

00:16:29.640 --> 00:16:31.280
will be investigated by the police.

00:16:31.280 --> 00:16:33.280
The killer will not escape justice.

00:16:35.280 --> 00:16:36.810
Just like Master taught us,

00:16:38.040 --> 00:16:38.960
in every case,

00:16:39.640 --> 00:16:41.170
as long as you keep digging,

00:16:41.840 --> 00:16:42.520
the truth

00:16:43.560 --> 00:16:44.640
will come to light.

00:16:54.680 --> 00:16:55.440
Don't leave town

00:16:55.440 --> 00:16:56.280
for a while.

00:16:56.440 --> 00:16:57.080
Okay.

00:16:57.120 --> 00:16:58.280
We'll notify you if anything comes up.

00:16:58.280 --> 00:16:59.520
Okay.

00:17:00.680 --> 00:17:02.360
Next time you want me to come for good tea,

00:17:02.360 --> 00:17:03.520
tell me in advance.

00:17:03.720 --> 00:17:04.720
I'll bring my own.

00:17:24.800 --> 00:17:25.400
Oh, my.